## Frontend env (Vite)
#
# Leave empty to use same-origin requests:
# - in dev, `vite.config.ts` proxies API routes to `http://localhost:5050`
# - in prod, set this if your API is hosted on a different origin
#
# Examples:
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5050
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.example.com
VITE_API_URL=

